\id 2TH - Baibal Kathoung New Testament 
\h 2 THESALON 
\toc1 2 THESALON 
\toc2 2 Thesalon 
\toc3 2 Th 
\mt1 2 THESALON  
\mt2 (The Second Epistle of Paul to the Thessalonians)  
\c 1  
\s1 Lawk karouknae  
\p
\v 1 Pawl, Silvanas, hoi Timote tinaw ni, maimae Pa Cathut hoi Bawipa Jisuh Khrih dawk kaawm e Thesalon kho kaawm Kawhmoun koe ca na patawn awh.  
\v 2 Bawipa Jisuh Khrih hoi maimae Pa Cathut koehoi e lungmanae hoi lungmawngnae teh nangmouh koe awm lawiseh.   
\s1 Cathut lawkcengnae  
\p
\v 3 Hmaunawnghanaw, nangmae yuemnae teh, puenghoi a roung teh, buet touh hoi buet touh lengkaleng lungpatawnae hoi na kawi awh dawkvah, kaimouh ni sak hane kawi lah ao e patetlah nangmouh kecu dawk Cathut lungmanae teh pout laipalah ka pholen awh.  
\v 4 Hottelah nangmouh ni rektapnae, rucat kâhmonae pueng hah na khang awh laihoi, na yuemnae ka hmu navah, Cathut e kawhmounnaw koe nangmouh na kâoupkhai awh.   
\p
\v 5 Nangmouh ni, Cathut uknaeram hanelah, reithai na khang awh teh, hote ram thung kâen hanlah na kamcu toe tie hah panue sak nahan, kalan lah Cathut e lawkcengnae teh hottelah hoi a kamnue sak.  
\v 6 Cathut ni kalanlah a sak han. Nangmouh runae na ka poe koe runae a pha sak vaiteh,  
\v 7 Runae kâhmo e nangmouh hoi kaimouh koevah kâhatnae na poe awh han.  
\v 8 Bangtelamaw tetpawiteh, Bawipa Jisuh Khrih teh bahu kaawm e kalvantaminaw hoi kalvan kho hoi a kum toteh, Cathut kapanuekhoehnaw hoi Bawipa Jisuh Khrih e kamthang kahawi ka thai ngai hoeh e naw pueng teh, hmai hoi runae a poe han.  
\v 9 Bawipa Jisuh teh a tami kathoungnaw lahoi amae thao bawilennae a kamnue e hai thoseh, kaimae lawkpanuesaknae na yuem awh dawkvah,  
\v 10 kayuemnaw pueng lahoi kângairu pholennae hai thoseh, coe hanelah a tho na hnin vah, ahnimouh teh Bawipa e hmaitung bawilennae koehoi kapek vaiteh, a yungyoe rawknae hoi reknae hah a khang awh han.   
\p
\v 11 Hatdawkvah, maimae Cathut hoi Bawipa Jisuh Khrih e a lungmanae patetlah Bawipa Jisuh Khrih e Min teh nangmouh koehoi bawilennae a kamnue nahanelah thoseh, nangmouh hai Bawipa koehoi bawilen a kamnue nahanelah thoseh, nangmouh teh kaw e lah na kamcu awh tie panuek awh nateh,  
\v 12 hno kahawi sak han lungthonae pueng hoi, na yuemnae koe bawilennae bahu hoi akawi nahanlah kaimouh ni nangmouh hanlah pou ka ratoum awh.   
\c 2  
\s1 Rawknae capa  
\p
\v 1 Hmaunawnghanaw, Bawipa Jisuh Khrih a tho nahane hoi ama koe maimouh cungtalah kamkhueng nahane hoi ka kâkuenlah,  
\v 2 Muitha lahoi thoseh, a lawk pâphonae lahoi thoseh, ca na patawn awh e lahoi thoseh, Bawipa e hnin teh yo a tho toe telah a dei awh eiteh, lungpuen tâsuenae tang na tawn awh hoeh nahanlah na dei pouh ngai awh.  
\v 3 Apini hai bangpatetlah hoi hai kâdum sak hanh awh. Hote hnin a pha hoehnahlan kâkapeknae hmaloe awm vaiteh, tamikahawihoehe rawknae capa teh a tâco han.  
\v 4 Ahni teh Cathut hoi bawknae pueng hah a taran vaiteh, amahoima kârasang vaiteh, Cathut e bawkim dawk tahung vaiteh, amahoima Cathut doeh telah a kâpathang han.   
\p
\v 5 Nangmouh hoi rei ka o awh navah hote kongnaw yo ka dei awh e hah na pâkuem awh hoeh maw  
\v 6 Ahni teh amae tue nah a tâco nahanelah, atuvah ka ngang e ao tie hai na panue awh.  
\v 7 Bangtelamaw tetpawiteh, kâlawklaipanae arulawk teh, atuvah a kâroe lahun toe. Hatei kangangkung takhoe lah ao hoehroukrak a ngang han.  
\v 8 Takhoe lah ao torei teh kâlawklaipa e tami a kamnue han. Hote tami kahawihoehe hah Bawipa Jisuh ni amae muitha lawk lahoi raphoe vaiteh, a kumnae raeng hoi a takhoe han.  
\v 9 Rawknae koe ka phat hane taminaw koevah hote tami kahawihoehe a thonae teh, Setan e thawtawknae lahoi dumyennae bahu, mitnoutnae, kângairu hno aphunphun hoi, kamsoumhoehe dumyennae aphunphun hoi a tho han.  
\v 10 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ahnimouh teh, rungngang lah o nahanelah, lawkkatang lungpataw hane ngai awh hoeh.  
\v 11 Hatdawkvah, lawkkatang hah yuem laipalah, kamsoumhoehe hno dawk kahring e naw pueng teh,  
\v 12 lawkkatang ka yuem hoeh niteh lanhoehnae dawk kaawmnaw hah yonphukhangsak nahane doeh.   
\s1 Kacaklah kangdue hanlah lawkthuinae  
\p
\v 13 Hateiteh, Bawipa ni lungpataw e hmaunawnghanaw, nangmouh teh thoungsaknae, lawkkatang yuemnae lahoi rungngangnae dawk pha hanelah Cathut ni hmaloe hoiyah na rawi awh toung dawkvah, nangmouh kecu dawk kaimouh ni Cathut lungmanae pout laipalah ka pholen awh han.  
\v 14 Hot patetlah hanelah kamthang kahawi lahoi nangmouh teh na kaw awh toe. Bangkongtetpawiteh, nangmouh teh, Bawipa Jisuh Khrih e bawilennae hmawngkhai nahanelah doeh.  
\v 15 Hatdawkvah hmaunawnghanaw, lawk lahoi hai thoseh, ca lahoi hai thoseh, kaimouh ni na cangkhai awh e lawkkatang dawk kacaklah kangdout awh nateh na lungpen awh.   
\p
\v 16 Maimanaw lungpataw niteh, a yungyoe lungpahawinae, lungmanae lahoi kahawi e ngaihawinae na ka poe e, maimae Pa Cathut hoi maimae Bawipa Jisuh Khrih ama roeroe ni,  
\v 17 nangmae lungthin a dam sak teh, lawk kahawi, hnokahawi pueng dawk nangmanaw hah na caksak awh naseh.   
\c 3  
\s1 Ratoum pouh awh  
\p
\v 1 Ahnoungpoung lah, hmaunawnghanaw, Bawipa e lawkkatang teh, nangmouh koe a kâkahei teh Bawilennae a kamnue e patetlah hmuen tangkuem koehai a kamnue thai nahanelah,  
\v 2 ka kaisue niteh tami kahawihoehe naw kut dawk hoi ka hlout awh thai nahan kaimouh hanelah na ratoum pouh awh.  
\v 3 Hatei, Bawipa teh yuemkamcu e lah ao. Nangmouh na caksak awh vaiteh kahawihoehe hno pueng dawk hoi hlout nahanelah na kabawp awh han.  
\v 4 Kaimouh ni kâ na poe e patetlah nangmouh ni na tarawi awh. Hmalah haiyah bout na tarawi awh han doeh titeh Bawipa kâuep laihoi oupvoutnae ka tawn awh hoeh.  
\v 5 Cathut lungpataw sak nahanelah thoseh, Khrih patetlah hring sak nahanelah thoseh, Bawipa ni nangmae lung hah hroecoe lawiseh.   
\s1 Pangak hoeh nahanlah kâhruetcuet poenae  
\p
\v 6 Hmaunawnghanaw kaimouh koe na kamtu awh e patetlah tarawi laipalah hno kamsoumhoeh lah ka sak e hmaunawnghanaw pueng hah roun awh tie hah maimae Bawipa Jisuh Khrih min lahoi kâ na poe awh.  
\v 7 Bangkongtetpawiteh kaimouh ni ka tawksak e patetlah nangmouh ni bangtelamaw ka tawksak han tie teh na panue awh. Kaimouh ni hno kamsoumhoehlah ka sak awh hoeh.  
\v 8 Apie rawca hai ka cat rumram awh hoeh. Nangmouh thung dawk buet touh boehai na tarawk awh hoeh nahanlah patangpalai laihoi kâyawm awh teh karum khodai thaw ka tawk awh.  
\v 9 Hottelah ka saknae teh hmu han ka ngai awh dawk nahoeh. Nangmanaw ni kamtu hanelah ka tawksak awh e doeh.  
\v 10 Bangkongtetpawiteh nangmouh hoi rei ka o navah ka pangak e teh rawca hai cat nahanh seh telah kâ na poe awh.  
\v 11 Hno kamsoumhoeh lah ka sak niteh banghai tawk laipalah, ma hoi kâkuen hoeh e dawk ka kambawng e tami tangawn na o awh tie ka thai awh.  
\v 12 Hot patet e taminaw koe mae rawca, ca thai nahanelah lungmawng lahoi thaw na tawk thai nahan, Bawipa Jisuh Khrih ni kâ na poe e patetlah tha na poe awh,  
\v 13 Hmaunawnghanaw hnokahawi na sak awh navah lungpoutnae tawn hanh awh.   
\p
\v 14 Hete ca lahoi lawk na thui e patetlah tami buetbuet touh ni tarawi hoehpawiteh, yeirai po nahanelah kâhuikokhai awh hanh.  
\v 15 Hatei hote tami hah taran telah pouk a hanh awh. Hmaunawngha patetlah pouk awh, hroecoe awh.   
\s1 Lawkthuinae  
\p
\v 16 Roumnae Bawipa ama roeroe ni bangtelae hmuen koe na pha hai thoseh, nangmouh koe lungmawngnae na poe lawiseh. Bawipa teh nangmouh abuemlah koe awm lawiseh.  
\v 17 Hete kutmannae ca heh kai Pawl roeroe ni ka kut hoi ka thut e doeh. Hathateh, ca kathut e pueng dawk e mitnout e lah ao. Kai ni hettelah ouk ka thut.  
\v 18 Maimae Bawipa Jisuh Khrih e lungmanae teh nangmouh pueng koe awm lawiseh. Amen.   